{% block description %}
    <p>
        Aimeos is a full-featured online shop and market place bundle which
        integrates the Aimeos e-commerce library into Symfony. It offers a
        complete and fully tested set of shop components for Symfony with a
        strong focus on flexibility, performance, scalibility, usability and
        software quality.
        The bundle provides components for e.g. faceted search, product lists and
        detail views as well as baskets, the checkout process, e-mails handling
        and "MyAccount" components. It supports 60+ payment providers using the
        Omnipay payment library and offers interfaces for ERP, CRM, PIM and
        similar systems.
        A full demo setup including routes is available for a quick start.
    </p>
